4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the decomposition of quantization error and proposes a new method for quantizing norms, which is related to data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses similarity search for multimedia data, which is a common topic in multimedia research.
